title: Partitions of real intervals
content: Based on the theorems of the fourierdlem* series of GS's mathbox.

blocks.name: ciccp
blocks.content: Extend class notation with the partitions of a closed interval of extended reals.
blocks.origin: const class ciccp { RePart }

blocks.name: diff.ciccp.s
diff.ciccp.c
diff.ciccp.w
df-iccp
blocks.content: Define partitions of a closed interval of extended reals. Such partitions are finite increasing sequences of extended reals. (Contributed by AV, 8-Jul-2020.)

blocks.name: iccpval
blocks.content: Partition consisting of a fixed number ` M ` of parts. (Contributed by AV, 9-Jul-2020.)
blocks.origin:

  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s1, c0)
} = {
  fvmptd(hs0, ciccp, c0, crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))), cn, crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, cv(hs0))), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, cv(hs0)), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))), universe, wcel(c0, cn))
  a1i(wcel(c0, cn), wceq(ciccp, cmpt(hs0, cn, crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, cv(hs0))), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, cv(hs0)), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))))))
  df-iccp(hs0, s0, s1)
  adantl(wcel(c0, cn), wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wceq(crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, cv(hs0))), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, cv(hs0)), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))), crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1)))))))

  oveq2d(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, cv(hs0)), co(nat0, cfz, c0), wceq(cv(hs0), c0))
  oveq2(cv(hs0), c0, nat0, cfz)
  raleqdv(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, cv(hs0)), co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))
  oveq2(cv(hs0), c0, nat0, cfzo)
  id(wcel(c0, cn))
  a1i(wcel(c0, cn), wcel(crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))), universe))
  rabex(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1)))))
  ovex(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(crab(s0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s1, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1)), clt, cfv(cv(s0), co(cv(s1), caddc, nat1))))))
  diff.hs0.c(cn)

  diff.co.s(s0, cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, cv(hs0)))

blocks.pretty:
thm iccpval(setvar s0, setvar s1, class c0) {
  ‚ä¢ (c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï ‚Üí(RePart ` c0)= { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))})
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s1)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, c0)
} = {
  fvmptd(hs0, ciccp, c0, { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))}, cn, { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]hs0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]hs0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))}, universe, c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï)
  a1i(c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï, RePart =(hs0 ‚àà ‚Ñï ‚Ü¶ { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]hs0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]hs0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))}))
  df-iccp(hs0, s0, s1)
  adantl(c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï, hs0 = c0, { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]hs0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]hs0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))} = { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))})
  rabeqbidv(s0, (‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]hs0)), (‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0)), hs0 = c0, ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]hs0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1))), ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1))))
  oveq2d(cxr, cmap, (0[...]hs0), (0[...]c0), hs0 = c0)
  oveq2(hs0, c0, nat0, cfz)
  raleqdv(s1, (0[..^]hs0), (0[..^]c0), hs0 = c0, (s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))
  oveq2(hs0, c0, nat0, cfzo)
  id(c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï)
  a1i(c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï, { s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))} ‚àà ùïå)
  rabex(s0, (‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0)), ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1))))
  ovex(cxr, cmap, (0[...]c0))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c({ s0 ‚àà(‚Ñù*[‚Ü¶](0[...]c0))| ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà(0[..^]c0),(s0 ` s1)[<](s0 `(s1[+]1)))})
  diff.hs0.c(cn)
  diff.hs0.w(c0 ‚àà ‚Ñï)
  diff.co.s(s0, cxr, cmap, (0[...]hs0))
  diff.co.s(s0, nat0, cfz, hs0)
  diff.co.s(s0, cxr, cmap, (0[...]c0))
  diff.cxr.s(s0)
  diff.cmap.s(s0)
  diff.co.s(s0, nat0, cfz, c0)
  diff.nat0.s(s0)
  diff.cfz.s(s0)
  diff.wceq.s(s0, hs0, c0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.co.s(s1, nat0, cfzo, hs0)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s1)
  diff.co.s(s1, nat0, cfzo, c0)
  diff.nat0.s(s1)
  diff.cfzo.s(s1)
}

blocks.name: iccpart
blocks.content: A special partition. Corresponds to ~ fourierdlem2 in GS's mathbox. (Contributed by AV, 9-Jul-2020.)
blocks.origin:
thm iccpart(setvar s0, class c0, class c1) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, cn), wb(wcel(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0)), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(s0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)))))))
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c1)
} = {
  syl6bb(wcel(c0, cn), wcel(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0)), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(s0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1))))), wcel(c1, crab(hs0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), clt, cfv(cv(hs0), co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)))))))
  eleq2d(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0), crab(hs0, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), clt, cfv(cv(hs0), co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1))))), wcel(c0, cn))
  iccpval(hs0, s0, c0)
  elrab(hs0, c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), clt, cfv(cv(hs0), co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)))), wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(s0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)))))
  ralbidv(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wbr(cfv(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), clt, cfv(cv(hs0), co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1))), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(s0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1))))
  breq12d(cfv(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), clt, cfv(cv(hs0), co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)), cfv(c1, cv(s0)), cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)), wceq(cv(hs0), c1))
  fveq1(cv(hs0), c1, cv(s0))
  fveq1(cv(hs0), c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0)))
  diff.hs0.w(wral(s0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(s0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(s0), caddc, nat1)))))
  diff.wceq.s(s0, cv(hs0), c1)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
}

thm iccpartimp(class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  |- wi(w3a(wcel(c0, cn), wcel(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0)), wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0))), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1)))))
} = {
  3imp(wcel(c0, cn), wcel(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0)), wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0)), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1)))))
  syl6bi(wcel(c0, cn), wcel(c1, cfv(ciccp, c0)), wi(wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0)), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1))))), wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(hs0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1))))))
  iccpart(hs0, c0, c1)
  jctild(wa(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(hs0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1))))), wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0)), wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1))))
  adantl(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(hs0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1)))), wi(wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0)), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1)))))
  expcom(wral(hs0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1)))), wcel(c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0)), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1))))
  rspcva(hs0, c2, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1))), wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1))))
  breq12d(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1)), cfv(c1, c2), cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1)), wceq(cv(hs0), c2))
  fveq2(cv(hs0), c2, c1)
  fvoveq1(cv(hs0), c2, c1, caddc, nat1)
  simpl(wcel(c1, co(cxr, cmap, co(nat0, cfz, c0))), wral(hs0, co(nat0, cfzo, c0), wbr(cfv(c1, cv(hs0)), clt, cfv(c1, co(cv(hs0), caddc, nat1)))))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(c2)
  diff.hs0.c(co(nat0, cfzo, c0))
  diff.hs0.w(wbr(cfv(c1, c2), clt, cfv(c1, co(c2, caddc, nat1))))
}

blocks.name: iccpartleu
blocks.content: If there is a partition, then all intermediate points and the lower and the upper bound are less than or equal to the upper bound. (Contributed by AV, 14-Jul-2020.)

blocks.name: iccpartiun
blocks.content: A half-open interval of extended reals is the union of the parts of its partition. (Contributed by AV, 18-Jul-2020.)

blocks.name: icceuelpart
blocks.content: An element of a partitioned half-open interval of extended reals is an element of exactly one part of the partition. (Contributed by AV, 19-Jul-2020.)

blocks.name: iccpartdisj
blocks.content: The segments of a partitioned half-open interval of extended reals are a disjoint collection. (Contributed by AV, 19-Jul-2020.)

} = {
